Set Up and Manage Products that You Can Add On to Financial Services Cloud.

To get any of these add-ons, talk to your Salesforce Account Executive.

Financial Services Cloud Experience Cloud Sites

Provide partners and customers with access to Financial Services Cloud through Experience Cloud licenses for external users. With Experience Cloud, you can give access to a clientâ€™s profile, including account details, financial accounts, and more.

CRM Analytics for Financial Services

Gives financial advisors and personal bankers a comprehensive customer intelligence solution based on the CRM Analytics platform.

Data Cloud for Financial Services Cloud

Connects and integrates client data to give financial institutions a unified view of their clients.

Revenue Intelligence for Financial Services

Get predictions about Retail Management and Wealth Management customers who are likely to churn. Identify Wealth Management customers likely to add more assets in a specific period.

Salesforce Scheduler

Provides personalized experiences by precision-scheduling appointments with the right person at the right place and time.

Securing Your Data with Salesforce Shield

Protects data at rest, monitors usage, and prevents malicious activity.

Marketing Cloud Engagement

Creates and sends emails using customizable email templates to save time and send personalized emails to clients.

Account Engagement in Financial Services Cloud

Access Marketing Cloud Account Engagement (Pardot), a full suite of marketing tools.

Intelligent Document Automation for Financial Services Cloud

Simplifies the document management process, reduces manual data entry, and gets customer-submitted information faster using the Intelligent Form Reader.

Intelligent Form Reader for Financial Services Cloud

Provides optical character recognition to automatically extract data from financial documents.

Intelligent Document Reader for Financial Services Cloud

Uses Amazon Textract with AWS account to automatically extract data from documents and map fields to Salesforce object fields.

Einstein Bots

Provide customers with intelligent, self-service bots that integrate with your Salesforce data in a few clicks.
title: Financial Services Cloud Add-Ons Guide
